  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  18 years or older

          -  Undergoing benign gynecologic surgery via an exploratory laparotomy

          -  Capable of giving consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Oromaxillary or mental disturbances that would make chewing gum dangerous with regards
             to mastication or aspiration

          -  Intubated or unconscious when leaving the OR

          -  Bowel resection performed at the time of surgery

          -  Active bowel disease (IBD, appendicitis, etc)

          -  Gynecologic malignancy
      </textblock>
